This 2021, remember to be truly grateful for the air that you breathe and turn every part of your life into gold. The Secret Planet Earth inspirations is a gift from The Secret team to help us all find gratitude with everything around us. Watch The Secret again to uncover the magic on Planet Earth and to attract its wonder with Gratitude: https://visit.thesecret.tv/The-Secret-Film or click the link in the bio.

For an immersive experience listen to it on Audiobook, read by Rhonda herself: https://visit.thesecret.tv/TGS-audio or find out by clicking on the link in our profile.

node.text: If you meet someone who has qualities you wish you had, love those qualities and feel good about those qualities in that person, and you are bringing those qualities to yourself.⁠

node.text: Lori S. from Florida shared with us in The Secret of the Week about how even when you lose faith in yourself, the law of attraction never stops working and you can learn again to manifest your dream life. Read here this incredible story of losing and refinding faith: https://visit.thesecret.tv/KgenC4 or click the link in the bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Secret on July 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'WHAT YOU LOVE? CHOOSE'.

node.text: The purpose of your life is to choose the things you love and turn away from the things you don't love so you don't choose them. What do you love?⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Secret on July 24, 2021. May be a drawing of 1 person and text.

node.text: A man is but the product of his thoughts. What he thinks, he becomes. - Mahatma Gandhi. Learn how to create your life powerfully with daily wisdom at your fingertips with The Secret Daily Teachings App: https://visit.thesecret.tv/DT-App or click the link in the bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Secret on July 23, 2021. May be an illustration of bird and text.

node.text: Happiness comes from giving your full attention to thoughts that make you feel good and ignoring thoughts that don’t make you feel good.⁠
